{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/catchorg/Catch2/issues/1880","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/catchorg/Catch2","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/catchorg/Catch2/issues/1880/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/catchorg/Catch2/issues/1880/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/catchorg/Catch2/issues/1880/events","html_url":"https://github.com/catchorg/Catch2/issues/1880","id":576988318,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU1NzY5ODgzMTg=","number":1880,"title":"REQUIRE macro hides sign compare warnings (gcc/clang)","user":{"login":"danadam","id":170743,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3MDc0Mw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/170743?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam","html_url":"https://github.com/danadam","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/danadam/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":513091177,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw1MTMwOTExNzc=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/catchorg/Catch2/labels/Warnings%20issue","name":"Warnings issue","color":"f9d0c4","default":false,"description":null},{"id":719327170,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw3MTkzMjcxNzA=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/catchorg/Catch2/labels/Help%20wanted","name":"Help wanted","color":"0e8a16","default":false,"description":"Issue outside of the maintainers expertise"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2020-03-06T15:03:37Z","updated_at":"2020-03-19T08:52:52Z","closed_at":"2020-03-19T08:52:52Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"In the following code:\r\n```cpp\r\n#define CATCH_CONFIG_MAIN\r\n#include <catch.hpp>\r\n\r\nTEST_CASE(\"foo\")\r\n{\r\n    uint32_t u = 0;\r\n    int32_t i = -1;\r\n    if (u > i) printf(\"foo\\n\");    // line 8\r\n    REQUIRE(u > i);                // line 9\r\n    if (u > i) printf(\"foo\\n\");    // line 10\r\n}\r\n```\r\nWhen compiled with `-Wall` (gcc) or `-Wextra` (clang), it reports warnings on line 8 and 10 but not 9. See https://godbolt.org/z/W9wQqy :\r\n```\r\n<source>:8:11: error: comparison of integer expressions of different signedness: 'uint32_t' {aka 'unsigned int'} and 'int32_t' {aka 'int'} [-Werror=sign-compare]\r\n    8 |     if (u > i) printf(\"foo\\n\");\r\n      |         ~~^~~\r\n<source>:10:11: error: comparison of integer expressions of different signedness: 'uint32_t' {aka 'unsigned int'} and 'int32_t' {aka 'int'} [-Werror=sign-compare]\r\n   10 |     if (u > i) printf(\"foo\\n\");\r\n      |         ~~^~~\r\n```\r\n\r\nLooks like msvc reports warnings on all 3 lines, see https://godbolt.org/z/4uBsXT:\r\n```\r\n<source>(8): warning C4018: '>': signed/unsigned mismatch\r\n<source>(9): warning C4018: '>': signed/unsigned mismatch\r\n<source>(10): warning C4018: '>': signed/unsigned mismatch\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen you put parentheses around the expression, i.e., `REQUIRE((u > i))`, then gcc and clang report warning on that line too.","closed_by":{"login":"horenmar","id":9026413,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjkwMjY0MTM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9026413?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/horenmar","html_url":"https://gi